If you'd like you can just copy the Google Drive spreadsheet and document from links below. Important Note: you'll  have to tweak the Grading-Rubric-Script as described in the instructions, but otherwise these should be ready to go. Just copy these files when your into your Google account and they should appear on your Google Drive.

